<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ( rgẖm ḍyạʿ ạlḥb wṣwrth mn qlb ạlạ̹nsạn
 sẖạyfk ḥb ḥqyqy byndh ʿly̱ qlby ạlʿṭsẖạn )2
 ( ḥb wfyh gẖfrạn bạlnʿmẗ wạ̹ymạn )2
 ( yạlly ṣlybk fy ạlʿdl wfyh ạlrḥmẗ kmạn )2
 ( rgẖm ṣrạʿ ạlnfs ạlkạml jwh dwạyr ạldẖạt
 lmsẗ ạ̹ydk tsẖfy ạlnfs wtḥyy ạlqlb ạ̹n mạt )2
 ( ḥryẗ wtḥryr wạlrwḥ bạltgẖyr )2
 ( tʿln br ạllh wslạmh tʿln bdẖl ạldẖạt )2
 ( rgẖm ḥṣạr ạlsẖr wʿndh wzỷyr ạlsẖyṭạn
 sẖạyfk wạqf jnby wsẖạyf fy ạ̹ydyk ạlslṭạn )2
 ( lmạ ạlḥrb tzyd ạ̉nạ fy ạlṣkẖrẗ sẖdyd )2
 syf ạlrwḥ ạlklmẗ ạlḥy byḍmn nṣry ạlạ̉n
 ( rgẖm rnyyn ạlmạdẗ wʿnf rnyyn ạljsdyạt
 tyjy wtrfʿ qlby bnʿmẗ wtmnḥ rwḥy tẖbạt )2
 ( ṭwl mạ ạnạ tẖạbt fyk wf ḥbk wạ̹ydyk )2
 ( hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny ạlrḥlẗ bṭwlhạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ạltrnymạt )2</lyrics>
<title>rgẖm ḍyạʿ ạlḥb</title>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>1574</hymn_number>
</song>